<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 01:08:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在冲突中比特币徘徊在交易区间下限附近</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/bitcoin-tumbles-with-stocks-as-trump-signals-harder-iran-strikes</link><description>由于中东冲突的影响持续存在不确定性，比特币交易价格接近其一个多月交易区间的下限。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iemMEm5XlsqQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 04:10:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/bitcoin-tumbles-with-stocks-as-trump-signals-harder-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>窃取中本聪的比特币成为量子计算的威胁</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-02/stealing-satoshi-s-bitcoin-becomes-a-quantum-computing-threat</link><description>谷歌研究论文引发担忧&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itU5Gc2d.COg/v6/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-02/stealing-satoshi-s-bitcoin-becomes-a-quantum-computing-threat</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase 表示其信托宪章已获得美国有条件批准</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-says-it-wins-conditional-us-approval-for-trust-charter</link><description>美国最大的加密货币交易所 Coinbase Global Inc. 表示，其国家信托公司执照已获得银行监管机构有条件批准，此举可能为其拓展新业务铺平道路。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieCY.f6h1US8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 15:32:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-says-it-wins-conditional-us-approval-for-trust-charter</guid></item><item><title>比特币“鲸鱼”抛售削弱了机构需求</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-buying-fails-to-offset-a-wave-of-selling-by-big-holders</link><description>即使机构购买增加，比特币需求仍然面临压力，这表明更广泛的市场仍在抛售该代币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iuZpxHDg1q1s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 22:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-buying-fails-to-offset-a-wave-of-selling-by-big-holders</guid></item><item><title>价值 2.8 亿美元的加密货币黑客事件暴露了 DeFi 中的人为薄弱环节</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/solana-based-defi-project-drift-hit-by-285-million-exploit</link><description>Drift 是一个基于 Solana 区块链的去中心化金融项目，遭到黑客攻击，该协议损失了近 3 亿美元的数字资产，使其成为加密货币历史上最大的漏洞之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioQmeBKVq_zE/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:25:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/solana-based-defi-project-drift-hit-by-285-million-exploit</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase、Cloudflare、Stripe 推动塑造人工智能货币的未来</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-cloudflare-stripe-push-to-shape-future-of-ai-money</link><description>加密货币、支付和云基础设施领域的知名人士正在竞相为人工智能代理（而不是人类）处理互联网交易的世界构建金融管道。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihyFcJs4ngz4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-cloudflare-stripe-push-to-shape-future-of-ai-money</guid></item></channel></rss>